1 Avoid chemical or color your hair it will damage your hair and if you need to change your hair color change it with natural lemon juice or any other. 2  Use the right kind of comb. 3  Don't use a brush when hair is wet; wet hair tends to be weaker than dry hair. 4  The brush will only stretch out the hair and cause breakage. You can use olive oil to make your hair grow out super fast. 2  Make sure you rinse it out good after leaving it in for 10 minutes or so. 3  Buy silk pillow cases. 4  Cotton pillow cases not only make your hair frizzy but also absorb the moisture in your hair, leaving it dry.

